cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "RCGov — Mobius Reflective Context Governor"
message: "If you use this software, please cite it using the metadata below."
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Toeda
    given-names: Taiko
    affiliation: MOBIUS LLC
abstract: >-
  Local-first semantic hygiene and context governance for LLM systems:
  govern what a model is allowed to read before it answers. Ingests raw
  context, scans for secrets and prompt injection, proposes role/authority/
  temporal tags, applies provenance and non-compromise gates, and emits a
  governed Clean Pack plus audit reports.
